<section id="learn" class="learn"><article><h3>ATM versus GTM</h3><p>ATM includes the mass carried through the coupling. GTM is the mass carried through the caravan wheels when coupled.</p></article><article><h3>Towball uses payload</h3><p>Towball download adds to the tow vehicle’s loaded mass and can make the vehicle exceed GVM or its rear axle limit.</p></article><article><h3>The lowest rating wins</h3><p>Vehicle, towbar, coupling, axles, tyres and caravan ratings all matter. A strong total-mass result does not override a lower component limit.</p></article></section>
